romt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Neuro  MT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/19/02 9:37:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.houston.rr.com/neuromt/pwned.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flowing Thought Items?</span><hr size=1> Actually, the orb is different.  It has only 25hp, but can go in primary and secondary slots.<br><br>Items:<br><br>Wito Xi Tetoracu:  FT2 (Face)<br>Itraer Insignia: FT2 (Ranged)<br>Collar of Tavuel Xakreum: FT2 (Neck)<br>Crown of Narandi: FT2 (Head)<br>Grodan's Flowing Cape: FT2 (Back)<br>Veil of Hidden Thought: FT2 (Face)<br>White Dragonscale Boots: FT2 (Feet)<br>Brain of Cazic Thule: FT1 (Ranged)<br>Buckler of Insight: FT1 (Secondary)<br>Choker of the Wretched: FT1 (Neck)<br>Earring of Fond Memories: FT1 (Ear)<br>Eye of Cazic Thule: FT1 (Face)<br>Mask of the Silver Eyes: FT1 (Face)<br>Robe of Inspiration: FT1 (Chest)<br>Runed Coldain Prayer Shawl: FT1 (Shoulders)<br>Sal'Varae's Robe: FT1 (Chest)<br>Wand of Musing: FT1 (Primary)<br>White Dragon Idol: FT1 (Ranged)<br>White Dragon Statue: FT1 (Ranged)<br>Golden Leaf Earring: FT3 (Ear)<br>Helm of Grim Blessings: FT3 (Head)<br>Seer's Orb of Power: FT3 (Primary/Secondary/Ranged)<br>Geomantic Focus: FT3 (Ranged)<br>Warmaster's Mask of Battle: FT3 (Face)<br>Essence of Nature: FT5 (Secondary)<br>Shield of Ssraeshza: FT6 (Secondary)<br>Shield of the Creator: FT6 (Secondary)<br><br>I'm sure there's a few I missed, but that covers 90% of them.  According to this list, the max FT you can have as a Priest Class is FT25, and the max you can have as a Caster class is FT22. (Priests get the uber Earring from Tunare).  Supposedly there's a pair of FT3 gloves from Griegs for casters, which would make the score even. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ugrimmlokk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimmlokk</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/19/02 9:46:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flowing Thought Items?</span><hr size=1>  Damn I thought the orb had 100hp when we got it. It has none though.<br><br> Also there's a FT 1 held item and robe. Dunno what mob they're from.<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub38.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessage?topicID=20666.topic">pub38.ezboard.com/fmonkly...0666.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p><B><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6122>Grimmlokk</a>, Forlorn</B> <BR>Warlord of E'ci<BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/eq/Grimmlokk/fullsize/bunnysig.jpg><BR><B><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=7932>Pokewell Andoften</a>, Forlorn </B><BR>Blackguard of the 57th pilfer<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/udemorgoth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Demorgoth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF33>(2/21/02 6:01:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Max FT</span><hr size=1> Max total FT is 15 I believe. <br>Anything over that doesn't stack. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><t